<br />Also, in all seriousness. A general forum rule: People don't take too well to sig links that have nothing to do with the forum you are in. It's okay that you are passionate about selling some product (Shakeology), but if that is the only reason that you are here that is not okay.
<br />
<br />Perhaps you can post a link to your NESDev related website/blog in your signature, then provide a link to your shakeology somewhere there. I see nothing wrong with that. I do something similar, my NESDev youtube in some way or form links to my music projects.

		

